Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Laud Sitangkai Elementary School in the Municipality of Sitangkai, Province of Tawi-Tawi, to Panglima Alare Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 331
An Act Changing the Name of the Laud Sitangkai Elementary School in the Municipality of Sitangkai, Province of Tawi-Tawi, to Panglima Alare Elementary School
Section 1. The name of the Laud Sitangkai Elementary School in the Municipality of Sitangkai, Province of Tawi-Tawi, is changed to Panglima Alare Elementary School.1awp++i1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: January 19, 1983
